  "message": "\ud83d\udc1b Add missing @agentclientprotocol/sdk to server dependencies (#180)\n\nThe ACP SDK was imported in acp-manager.ts but not declared in\nserver/package.json, causing build failures on clean installs.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
